<div class="header">
	 <h1>图片系统</h1>
</div>
<div class="content">
	<h3 class="marketing-header">基础介绍</h3>
	<p>Tidy中的图片主要有两种,一种是非响应式图片,一种是响应式图片</p>
	<h3 class="marketing-header">响应式图片</h3>
	<p>响应式图片使用.tidy-img-responsive类</p>
	<div class="tidy-g">
		<div class="tidy-u-1-2">
			<img src="images/re1.JPG" class="tidy-img-responsive">
		</div>
		<div class="tidy-u-1-2">
			<img src="images/re2.JPG" class="tidy-img-responsive">
		</div>
	</div>
	<pre class="code code-wrap code-wrap-full"><code>&lt;div class="tidy-g"&gt;
	&lt;div class="tidy-u-1-2"&gt;
		&lt;img src="images/re1.JPG" class="tidy-img-responsive"&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class="tidy-u-1-2"&gt;
		&lt;img src="images/re2.JPG" class="tidy-img-responsive"&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
	<p>响应式图片是可以不用栅格布局的,在这里使用主要是为了分成两栏</p>
	<h3 class="marketing-header">非响应式图片</h3>
	<p>非响应式图片和Bootstrap里的一样,有三种:矩形,圆角矩形和圆形</p>
	<h3 class="marketing-subheader">矩形</h3>
	<p>使用.thumb类</p>
	<h3 class="marketing-subheader">圆角矩形</h3>
	<p>使用.thumb-rounded类</p>
	<h3 class="marketing-subheader">圆形</h3>
	<p>使用.thumb-circle类</p>
	<div style="background:rgb(255,255,255)" class="tidy-u-1">
		<img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="thumb">
		<img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="thumb-rounded">
		<img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="thumb-circle">
	</div>
	<pre class="code code-wrap code-wrap-full"><code><h1>&lt;div style="background:rgb(255,255,255)" class="tidy-u-1"&gt;
	&lt;img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="thumb"&gt;
	&lt;img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="thumb-rounded"&gt;
	&lt;img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="thumb-circle"&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</h1></code></pre>
	<h3 class="marketing-header">两者结合使用</h3>
	<div class="tidy-g">
		<div class="tidy-u-1-3">
			<img src="images/re1.JPG" class="tidy-img-responsive thumb">
		</div>
		<div class="tidy-u-1-3">
			<img src="images/re2.JPG" class="tidy-img-responsive thumb-rounded">
		</div>
		<div class="tidy-u-1-3">
			<img src="images/re3.JPG" class="tidy-img-responsive thumb-circle">
		</div>
	</div>
</div>